  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help redevelop Maunga school, Livingstone, Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Maunga Primary School is located in the rural Maunga community comprising of 8 villages and a population of a bit over 3000. Family income levels in this area are low, and so many children are growing up surrounded by extreme poverty.  Our aim is to increase the capacity of the school to offer higher learning possibilities for their pupils.  The school is severely resource-limited with classes that are over-crowded and lacking educational materials.</narrative>
  </description>
